Installation Instructions
*************************

Relies on VESmail -
git@github.com:vesvault/VESmail.git

Put the Android dir in VESmail/app dir (VESmail/app/VESmail-android),
or adjust the native code path.

libVES.so has to be built first -
git@github.com:vesvault/libVES.c.git
lib/Android.mk

curl and openssl libs are required to build both libVES.c and VESmail.
(libcurl, libcrypto, libssl)

Suggested prebuilt binaries:
git@github.com:robertying/openssl-curl-android.git
(use LOCAL_WHOLE_STATIC_LIBRARIES in libVES.c/lib/Android.mk)

Use Android Studio to build and deploy.
